seo: Draytek,CVE-2020-8515,漏洞检测,命令注入,高危
summary: 该插件用于检测Draytek设备中的CVE-2020-8515命令注入漏洞，通过发送特定payload验证是否存在漏洞并返回相关信息。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the CVE-2020-8515 command injection vulnerability in Draytek devices by sending a specific payload to verify the existence of the vulnerability and return related information.
